---
title: Agent Fan-Out — Phase 2 (Parallel Execution)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant OMIRTH as Orchestrator<br/>Mirth
    participant CR as claimreview-matcher
    participant CL as coverage-left
    participant CC as coverage-center
    participant CRR as coverage-right
    participant DE as domain-evidence
    participant GFCT as Google Fact Check<br/>Tools API
    participant NEWS as NewsAPI / GNews
    participant MBFC as Media Bias<br/>Fact Check
    participant PRIMARY as CDC / WHO /<br/>SEC / Courts

    Note over ORC,PRIMARY: Precondition: entity-extractor has emitted F-status.<br/>Orchestrator dispatches all five agents simultaneously.

    par Parallel MCP dispatch
        ORC->>CR: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_normalized, entities})
    and
        ORC->>CL: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_text, entities, reply_channel: "ORCH_ACK"})
    and
        ORC->>CC: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_text, entities, reply_channel: "ORCH_ACK"})
    and
        ORC->>CRR: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_text, entities, reply_channel: "ORCH_ACK"})
    and
        ORC->>DE: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_text, entities, domain, reply_channel: "ORCH_ACK"})
    end

    Note over CR,GFCT: ClaimReview Matcher (independent)

    CR->>GFCT: GET /factcheck/v1alpha1/claims:search<br/>?query=claim_normalized
    GFCT-->>CR: ClaimReview results[]

    CR->>CR: compute semantic match score<br/>select best match if score >= 0.75

    CR->>CR: tool: add_observation(CLAIMREVIEW_MATCH, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIMREVIEW_VERDICT, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIMREVIEW_SOURCE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIMREVIEW_MATCH_SCORE, F)

    CR->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK

    Note over CL,MBFC: Coverage Left (independent — same pattern for Center + Right)

    CL->>NEWS: GET articles?q=entities&from=source_date<br/>filter: left-spectrum outlets
    NEWS-->>CL: articles[]

    CL->>MBFC: GET bias ratings for outlet names
    MBFC-->>CL: bias_scores[]

    CL->>CL: analyze framing across article set<br/>select top credibility source

    CL->>CL: tool: add_observation(COVERAGE_ARTICLE_COUNT, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(COVERAGE_FRAMING, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE_URL, F)

    CL->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK

    Note over CC: Coverage Center — same flow as Coverage Left

    CC->>NEWS: article search (center outlets)
    CC->>MBFC: bias ratings
    CC->>CC: analyze + write OBX
    CC->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK

    Note over CRR: Coverage Right — same flow as Coverage Left

    CRR->>NEWS: article search (right outlets)
    CRR->>MBFC: bias ratings
    CRR->>CRR: analyze + write OBX
    CRR->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK

    Note over DE,PRIMARY: Domain Evidence (independent)

    DE->>DE: determine relevant primary source<br/>from CLAIM_DOMAIN and entities

    DE->>PRIMARY: fetch authoritative source document
    PRIMARY-->>DE: source content

    DE->>DE: evaluate alignment between<br/>source content and claim

    DE->>DE: tool: add_observation(DOMAIN_SOURCE_NAME, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(DOMAIN_SOURCE_URL, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(DOMAIN_EVIDENCE_ALIGNMENT, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(DOMAIN_CONFIDENCE, F)

    DE->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK

    Note over ORC: Orchestrator receives 5 ACKs.<br/>completion register: 5/5 parallel agents complete.<br/>Dispatches blindspot-detector (Phase 3a).
